"=How To Salute.= To salute, a Girl Scout raises           the right hand to her hat in line with the right           temple, the first three fingers extended, and the           little finger held down by the thumb.",0,0,0,0,0,0
This salute           is the sign of the Girl Scouts.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"The three extended           fingers, like the Trefoil, represent the three           parts of the Promise.",0,0,0,0,0,0
