"If in uniform a Girl Scout stands at attention and           salutes the flag when it is hoisted or lowered,           and as it passes her in parade.",1,0,0,0,0,0
"If not in uniform,           she stands at attention, but does not salute.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"When in uniform and in ranks in public           demonstration, a Girl Scout stands at attention           and salutes when the Star Spangled Banner is           played.",0,0,0,0,0,0
