_Planning Your House._ When you plan a house of your own you must think what it needs most.,1,0,0,0,0,0
"You would choose, first of all, to have abundant air, fresh and clean; a dry spot where dampness will not stay; sunshine at some time of day in every room of the house, which you can have if your house faces southeast; and you must be able to get a good supply of pure water.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"You will want to make your house warm in the winter and cool in the summer, so you will look out for windows, doors and porches.",1,0,0,0,0,0
"Think what must be done in a house: eating, sleeping, working, resting, by the whole family.",0,0,0,0,0,0
How many rooms must you have?,0,0,0,0,0,0
