_The Bedroom._ Your bedroom needs all the fresh air it can get.,1,0,0,0,0,0
The Girl Scout sleeps with her windows open.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"As soon as you have dressed in the morning throw the windows wide open again, if they have been closed.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"Open the bed, so that both sheets may be reached by the fresh air.",0,0,0,0,0,0
Shake up your pillows and put them on a chair near the window.,0,0,0,0,0,0
Leave your night clothing spread or hung where it will be well aired.,0,0,0,0,0,0
Let your room have a fresh air bath!,0,0,0,0,0,0
You know already how to make a bed.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"You will remember that all the bedclothing must be smooth and even, when the bed is made.",0,0,0,0,0,0
