Fighting the House Fly and Mosquito House flies carry disease.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"They breed in filth, human waste, animal droppings, decayed animal or vegetable matter, and are so made that they carry filth wherever they go.",1,0,0,0,0,0
"Since the fly alights wherever it pleases, it carries dirt from outside and distributes it wherever it CHOOSES.",1,0,0,0,0,0
Clean up all heaps of rubbish where flies may breed.,0,0,0,0,0,0
