"Leave no still water even in an old tin can, for the eggs of mosquitoes are deposited in still water and hatch there.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"The mosquito, like many other insects, has an intermediate stage between the egg and the grown mosquito.",0,0,0,0,0,0
