TOAST--Good toast is worth knowing how to make.,0,0,0,0,0,0
The cook should not be satisfied with toast which is either white or burned.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"Toast is most easily made from stale bread, which should be cut in one-third to one-half inch slices.",0,0,0,0,0,0
A single slice of toast may be made by holding it over the fire on a fork.,1,0,0,0,0,0
In camp a forked stick answers every purpose.,0,0,0,0,0,0
