"Begin carefully and hold the bread some distance away from the fire, turning it often until it dries.",1,0,0,0,0,0
Then hold it nearer the coals until it a golden brown on both sides.,1,0,0,0,0,0
With a new coal fire or wood fire toast must be made on a toaster on the top of the stove to prevent the bread from being smoked.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"If the top of the stove is being used for other things, the drying may be done in the oven.",0,0,0,0,0,0
