"To Make an Unoccupied Bed Remove pillows and bedclothes, one at a time, being careful not to let corners drag on the floor, and put to air.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"Turn the mattress over from end to end one day, and from side to side next day.",0,0,0,0,0,0
