"An old blanket, old spread or a quilted pad, spread over the mattress not only protects the mattress but prevents the sheets from wearing out, and may make the bed more comfortable.",1,0,0,0,0,0
These should be kept clean.,0,0,0,0,0,0
The bed for a sick person is frequently made with a rubber sheet and a draw sheet.,0,0,0,0,0,0
The draw sheet is so called because its proper use is to be drawn through under the patient without greatly disturbing her and give her a cool fresh place to lie on.,1,1,1,1,1,1
