"Temperature, Pulse, Respiration The temperature of the average person in health is 98.6Â° Fahrenheit.",0,0,0,0,0,0
This is called the _normal_ temperature.,0,0,0,0,0,0
A temperature below 98.0 degrees is said to be sub-normal.,0,0,0,0,0,0
