"Using separate utensils, and a separate room for the sick person are two of the surest ways to prevent the spread of the disease.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"In such diseases as measles, scarlet fever, colds, mumps, influenza, dishes should be boiled every day.",0,0,0,0,0,0
Put them in a large kettle in cold water and let them come to a boil.,1,0,0,0,0,0
Even the thinnest glass will not break if treated in this way.,0,0,0,0,0,0
