"Heat the glass or spoon, put in some orange or lemon juice, then the oil, then more juice.",0,0,0,0,0,0
Open the mouth wide and put the oil far back.,0,0,0,0,0,0
Have more juice at hand to swallow immediately after.,0,0,0,0,0,0
