"_The Daily Clean-Out._--People, sick or well, should have a bowel movement once or twice a day.",0,0,0,0,0,0
Taking medicine for this purpose is a very bad habit.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"If healthy people have the proper exercise and food, and drink plenty of good water, medicine is not necessary.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"Eating coarse grained food, as bran muffins, corn meal porridge, fruits, and vegetables, drinking plenty of water, exercising in the open air, and having a regular time for going to the lavatory (immediately after breakfast and the last thing at night before retiring are suggested times) are habits that are usually sufficient to keep the bowels in good order.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"If the waste matter is not carried off by the bowel movements, the body will in time become poisoned by the decayed substance in the intestines, and illness follows.",0,0,0,0,0,0
