"You have probably heard of germs, microbes and bacteria.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"These are names for the same organisms, which are tiny forms of plant life unseen by the eye, and of which our unaided senses give us no knowledge.",0,0,0,0,0,0
They exist everywhere and in many forms.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"Most of them are harmless to human life, and many of them are useful, as, for example, one that grows on the roots of peas and beans and helps the plants to extract nitrogen from the air.",1,0,0,0,0,0
