"_Teeth_--Next to a fresh, sweet skin the most beautiful feature of a truly beautiful woman is her teeth.",1,1,1,1,0,0
The basis of beautiful teeth is a clean mouth.,0,0,0,0,0,0
Teeth should be brushed at least twice a day.,0,0,0,0,0,0
The best times are after breakfast and the last thing before going to bed.,0,0,0,0,0,0
