"If the well is near a stable or out house, or if dish water is thrown near it, let it alone.",1,0,0,0,0,0
"A well in sandy soil is more or less filtered by nature, but rocky or clayey earth may conduct disease germs a considerable distance under ground.",0,0,0,0,0,0
