The best form of grate is one with folding legs.,0,0,0,0,0,0
After laying the fire the legs of the grate are driven into the ground.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"As the fire burns down, the grate may be lowered by driving the legs in deeper.",0,0,0,0,0,0
This is a very useful utensil for supporting hot water pails or frying pan.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"When no forks can be found use the Pine Tree Horse, as shown in cut.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"In order to boil water hard it will only be necessary to slip the kettle down the pole, holding it in place by graduated notches.",1,0,0,0,0,0
