"If wanted only as an adjuvant to soups, stews, rice, macaroni, etc., the more concentrated puree will serve very well.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"Canned corn (better still, 'kornlet,' which is concentrated milk of sweet corn) is quite nourishing, and everybody likes it.",1,0,0,0,0,0
