"Limes are more compact and better medicinally, but they do not keep well.",1,0,0,0,0,0
"Lime juice in bottles is excellent, if you carry it.",1,0,0,0,0,0
"Citric acid crystals may be used in lieu of lemons when going light, but the flavor is not so good as that of lemonade powder that one can put up for himself.",1,1,1,1,1,1
